::  YouPaintFutaPaintingAnusDescription
You take your thick brush and paint from the <<= either("center of the anus outward in all directions", "outside to the center of the anus in all directions", "left side to the right side of the anus", "top to the bottom of the anus")>>.  The cool touch of the paint makes your canvas' anus twitch.  You want to make sure you've completely covered it in $you_paint_futa_current_color so you apply <<= either(3, 4, 5, 6)>> coats while it's still wet.
